### Hero Image Generation

Will use the `generate_image` tool with this prompt:
> "A clean, flat-style SaaS dashboard mockup illustration showing a learning management system interface with analytics graphs, student cards, and a sidebar. Use a cyan (#0ea5e9) and teal (#06b6d4) color palette on a dark background. Minimalist, modern, premium feel. No text. No device frames."

The generated image will be saved to `public/images/` and referenced in the hero section.

